The Texas Democratic Party told the DCNF that they do ‚Äúnot comment on specific candidates right before a primary that we are administering,‚Äù and the Pennsylvania Democratic Party did not respond to questions. Both states‚Äô economies are heavily dependent on the fossil fuel industry.
Democratic Rep. Max Rose of New York has come out in recent months against the GND, telling USA Today in April 2019 that Ocasio-Cortez‚Äôs solution to climate change is a ‚Äúmassive socialist economic policy platform. Just not needed.‚Äù He went on to say that ‚Äúurgent and bold action‚Äù is needed.
