Sanders, for his part, revealed his own GND in August 2019, promising everything from ‚Äúvirtually free‚Äù electricity and a ‚Äúhunger-free‚Äù transition to green energy from fossil fuels. The democratic socialist‚Äôs nearly 14,000-page memo also lays out how he will deal with a variety of social justice issues.
Republicans in the Senate torpedoed Ocasio-Cortez‚Äôs legislation in March 2019 as Democrats called the vote a dog-and-pony show. The GOP defeated the proposal 57-0; Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell called the bill a socialistic ploy designed to kill the economy. None of the Democratic senators supported the bill.
Ocasio-Cortez‚Äôs GND sought to phase out fossil fuel usage within 12 years, which would have cost tens of trillions of dollars, some reports show. Americans could be forced to pay up to $93 trillion to implement the proposal over a decade, the conservative-leaning American Action Forum (AAF) noted in a study in February 2019.
